data.description:
Beautiful family home in the heart of Poquoson, with freshly updated kitchen including stainless appliances, granite, and new cabinets. Hardwood floors, first floor master, and energy saving cellular shades in windows. Fresh paint and carpet throughout, new lvp, and vanities in upstairs bathrooms. 4 bedrooms upstairs with walk-in closets. Full laundry room, spacious garage with storage area, shed out back, new wood fence, and a screened porch off the eat-in kitchen. Walk or bike to our highy rated schools, the Poquoson Museum and gardens, and the marsh walking trails by Topping Creek.

Rental agreement for 1 year (12 months) or 2 years (24 months), after which tenant can move to month-to-month basis, with 45 day notice of residency termination.
Renter responsible for all utilities, and yard maintenance. Grass to be kept short to discourage pests.
No smoking on the property. No fire on premises except for outside, in bbq grill or contained in metal firepit.
Pets allowed only with prior written approval from owner and one time fee of $300 (per pet).
No alteration of structure without prior written approval of owner, including but not limited to painting, hanging shelving, installing lighting or curtain hardware.
Parking in garage and driveway only, not on grass. Park on the street at your own risk.
Tenant must maintain and show proof of renter's insurance, personal property not covered by landlord's policy.
